Yvonne Jegede bụ onye na -eme ihe nkiri na Naịjirịa, onye na -emeputa ihe nkiri, onye nlereanya, na onye onyonyo;  ama ama maka imepụta 3 is company
O bilitere wee bụrụ onye ama ama mgbe ọ pụtara ihe nkiri na vidiyo egwu African Queen nke 2Face Idibia tinyere Annie Macaulay
Yvonne Jegede was born in Agenebode, Edo State, Nigeria on the 25th of August, 1983
Ọ gụrụ agụmakwụkwọ praịmarị na secondiri na Lagos State Naịjirịa tupu ịga  University of Cyprus, ebe ọ nwetere akwukwo Bachelor's degree na International Relations.
Yvonne Jegede malitere ọrụ ihe nkiri ya na 2004 mgbe ọ pụtara na ihe nkiri Nollywood Missing Angels
Mpụta mbụ igwefoto mbụ ya pụtara na 2005 na ngosipụta ya na vidiyo egwu a ma ama ugbu a African Queen nke 2Face Idibia
Mgbe ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ mahadum n'afọ 2012, ọ bịaghachiri na Nollywood wee gosiputa na ihe nkiri dịka Okafor's Law Single and Married, 10 Days in Sun City n'etiti ndị ọzọ
Na 2015, ọ mepụtara ihe nkiri mbụ ya 3 is Company ebe ọ gosiputara bụrụ onye ndu
N'ọgwụgwụ 2016, ọ bụ mkpuchi na mbipụta agbamakwụkwọ nke magazin Genevieve Nnaji
Ewezuga ihe nkiri ya, Yvonne Jegede egosipụtala na vidiyo egwu dịka Ego site Djinee, Kokose nke Sound Sultan
